These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different nationalities: french, american
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: lacrosse, badminton
The people use 2 different means of transport: van, helicopter
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person driving the van##1
2. the american is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Nationality   | american    | french |
| Sport         | badminton | lacrosse    |
| Transport     | van     | helicopter      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, hot-chocolate
There are 2 different nationalities: russian, italian
The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, skateboard
1. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the russian is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate  | almond-milk   |
| Nationality   | italian | russian  |
| Transport     | skateboard   | boat |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: drawing, traveling
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: superhero, documentary
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: badminton, skiing
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is in an even position##4
2. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| Hobby         | drawing   | traveling  |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | superhero  |
| Sport         | badminton   | skiing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-4::.
