.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-7::.
There 2 different types of food: garlic, apple
The people have 2 different jobs:  paramedic, social-worker
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: basketball, swimming
1. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the paramedic##1
2. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is swimming##3
3. the person eating garlic is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | apple | garlic     |
| Job     | social-worker | paramedic |
| Sport   | swimming | basketball    |

 #################################

 
