.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-15::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: cooking, writing
There are 2 different nationalities: russian, japanese
2 different pets are kept: goldfish, hamster
1. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
2. the russian is on the left of the japanese##1
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Hobby         | writing | cooking |
| Nationality   | russian     | japanese     |
| Pet           | hamster          | goldfish     |

