.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-20::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: horror, epic
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: dubstep, house
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, subway
1. the person watching horror movies is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of house is on the right of the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | horror | epic |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep  | house  |
| Transport     | subway | airplane    |

 